result.name: Running Chicken

reviews.text: Great hot pot and good service
Dirty wash room. Very dirty
Cheesy chicken pot is the best and the portion is not small like the others, but the price is much reasonable. The table services is not bad but still have room for improvement.

This restaurant is an average one, the price is moderated, but don't expect any service.

The setup was not friendly to groups, like the pot is a small one, and they put the electronic furnace in the middle of the table for two.

In other words, if you have more to join the hot pot, you may want to get another pot to make it easier for the rest, otherwise it will be discouraged.

Highly recommend the tomato and corn soup base! The beef was super tender and the fish balls are great.
Slightly on the pricey side because you're ordering each thing individually, but you get what you pay for.

result.name: 米走雞

reviews.text: 芝士雞煲的雞沒有味道，雞煲只有雞，芝士等一段配料，很單調。醬油貴收14蚊人，但只是一開始提供八款供選擇。整體性價比不高。

非常推薦芝士雞煲！
雞的分量很多，也可以加芝士湯
喜歡麻辣的人可以吃麻辣雞煲（也有芝士）
配上不同配料非常好吃

一向都好中意食雞煲既我，今日終於約到朋友陪我一齊食芝士雞煲！
我跟朋友大概8點到達餐廳，餐廳座無虛席，非常熱鬧!坐低後，店員給予我們自助醬料調製醬汁，不過其實最後係唔需要用到的!
夜晚叫了芝士雞煲食，味道可以。 值得驚喜的是麻辣醬超好味（可問職員要）
比起芝士雞，個人更鍾意食麻辣雞😛😛😛
